433
00:41:19,821 --> 00:41:21,156
Lalu sekarang aku keluar.

434
00:41:21,573 --> 00:41:23,283
Lalu aku perlu tentara.

435
00:41:23,575 --> 00:41:27,704
Aku kenal satu orang.
